headline: Billionaire Warren Buffett Has Invested $91 Billion (at Cost) in These 2 Unstoppable Stocks
summary: Despite being a net seller of stocks to the tune of $166 billion over the last eight quarters, there are two premier stocks the Oracle of Omaha can't stop buying.
